{"type":null,"faqId":43718,"title":"如何使用亲情关怀功能？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body66607344\"><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p64374149\">请按如下步骤操作：</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p42496437\">1. 在主屏幕，点击“手机服务”。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p46923618\">2. 在“服务”页签下，点击“亲情关怀”。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p19659381\">3. 根据屏幕提示，点击“立即启用”，启用该服务。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p42716703\">4. 点击“添加亲友团”。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p48906009\">5. 从联系人列表中勾选要添加的亲友，然后点击“勾选”图标。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p37500900\">6. 根据需要，选择“发起邀请”或者“发起请求”。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p1963786\">7. 根据屏幕提示，双方建立远程连接。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033310368__p17674074\">需要对方手机也支持“亲情关怀”，目前华为大多数手机可以在华为应用市场下载“亲情关怀”来配合使用。</p></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0033310368","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399374000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":125,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"亲情关怀使用,亲情关怀功能,亲情关怀运用方法","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}